1
00:00:03,836 --> 00:00:09,019
It’s family life 
with Kṛṣṇa at the centre.

2
00:00:09,251 --> 00:00:19,347
So, for devotees—devotee families,
their life will be a happy one

3
00:00:19,347 --> 00:00:23,618
if Kṛṣṇa is at the centre
of everything.

4
00:00:23,758 --> 00:00:26,604
[Married Ashram]

5
00:00:26,964 --> 00:00:29,820
And this is something 
very extraordinary,

6
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:38,700
but if they will see one another 
as eternal servitors of Kṛṣṇa,

7
00:00:39,683 --> 00:00:45,563
superficially—husband, wife, child,
daughter, son—these things,

8
00:00:45,563 --> 00:00:53,945
but on a deeper … and that’s there,
it’s undeniable and there,

9
00:00:54,046 --> 00:01:01,269
but with the devotional eye awakened,
they’re able to see

10
00:01:01,269 --> 00:01:08,477
that who’s my child—
is a superior devotee than I.

11
00:01:08,523 --> 00:01:13,350
My child has more devotion
to Kṛṣṇa than I do.

12
00:01:13,697 --> 00:01:15,375
That’s possible.

13
00:01:15,375 --> 00:01:19,301
The husband of the wife;
the wife of the husband.

14
00:01:19,585 --> 00:01:25,236
They can see, as servitors,
their servitor identity.

15
00:01:25,236 --> 00:01:28,451
Bhakti Vinod Ṭhākur says
in one of his songs,

16
00:01:28,451 --> 00:01:32,007
“When this sort of genuine vision
is awakened,

17
00:01:32,007 --> 00:01:38,777
then caring for that family and other
necessities is also Kṛṣṇa bhakti—devotion,

18
00:01:38,777 --> 00:01:41,608
because you’re serving devotees.”

19
00:01:41,873 --> 00:01:46,233
‘If’, I say ‘if’ that …
we want it to be real.

20
00:01:48,382 --> 00:01:50,958
All these things are predicated.

21
00:01:50,958 --> 00:01:55,791
Sometimes Śrīla Guru Mahārāj presented
many, one of many things; he would say,

22
00:01:55,791 --> 00:01:57,929
“I suppose you want to know,

23
00:01:57,929 --> 00:02:01,019
how far is it real, 
how far is it true?”

24
00:02:01,019 --> 00:02:03,030
We could say anything.

25
00:02:03,030 --> 00:02:06,737
We can make any statement;
we can take any statement from the scriptures

26
00:02:06,737 --> 00:02:11,755
and apply it to anything,
but how far is it true, how far is it real?

27
00:02:11,755 --> 00:02:14,286
That we want to know. 
 

28
00:02:14,286 --> 00:02:26,079
But the possibility gives us some optimism, 
and encouragement, and inspiration.

